Interview Questions
What does map() do?

It iterates through an array and returns a new array.

Why use map() in React?

To render multiple UI elements from an array.

What is key?

A unique identifier used by React to efficiently update the DOM.

Can we use index as key?
key={index}

Yes, for learning and static lists.

For dynamic data:

key={employee.id}

is preferred.
